# Background Upload Progress Implementation Plan

Implement a global upload tracking system to provide real-time feedback and ensure uploads continue even if the UI components are unmounted (background feel).

## Proposed Changes

### [Component Name] Global State Management
#### [NEW] [UploadContext.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/contexts/UploadContext.tsx)
- Create a context to track active uploads.
- State: `{ [id: string]: { id: string; title: string; progress: number; status: 'uploading' | 'success' | 'error'; error?: string } }`
- Actions: `addUpload`, `updateProgress`, `completeUpload`.

### [Component Name] UI Components
#### [NEW] [UploadProgressOverlay.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/UploadProgressOverlay.tsx)
- A floating UI element (e.g., bottom-right) showing active upload percentages.
- Uses `UploadContext` to render progress bars and status icons.

#### [MODIFY] [CircleVideoComposer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoComposer.tsx)
- Integrate with `UploadContext` to show local progress or just delegate to the global overlay.

### [Component Name] Data Layer
#### [MODIFY] [useCircleVideos.ts](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/hooks/useCircleVideos.ts)
- Update `uploadVideo` mutation to emit progress events to `UploadContext`.
- Use Supabase `onUploadProgress` feature.

### [Component Name] App Root
#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/App.tsx)
- Wrap application with `UploadProvider`.
- Inject `UploadProgressOverlay` at the root level.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Open Circle Video Composer.
2. Select a video and click Publish.
3. Observe the progress percentage in the dialog/overlay.
4. Close the dialog immediately.
5. Verify that the upload continues in the background (overlay remains visible).
6. Verify that a success notification appears when 100% is reached.
